snippet.title: X4: Timelines - Official Story Trailer | Games Baked in Germany Showcase
snippet.description:
Embark on an unprecedented space odyssey with X4: Timelines, the latest addition to the X4 universe. It is your gateway to uncharted territories and untold stories. With a thrilling new storyline which takes place outside of the X4 sandbox, prepare yourself for colossal challenges and unexpected excursions into the depths of the X series lore and history.
Visit Steam and add X4: Timeless to your wishlist now!: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2700340/X4_Timelines/
